<p>おれと<span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>がしきりに<span class="vocab">赤シャツ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span><span class="vocab">退治<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>退治</rb><rt>たいじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;subjugation; subdual</span></span>の<span class="vocab">計略<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>計略</rb><rt>はかりごと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;planning; strategy</span></span>を<span class="vocab">相談して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>相談</rb><rt>そうだん</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;discuss</span></span>いると、<span class="vocab">宿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>宿</rb><rt>やど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lodgings</span></span>の<span class="vocab">婆さん<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>婆</rb><rt>ばあ</rt></ruby>さん&nbsp;old woman</span></span>が<span class="vocab">出て来て<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>て<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;appear; come in</span></span>、<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>の<span class="vocab">生徒<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生徒</rb><rt>せいと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;student</span></span>さんが<span class="vocab">一人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一人</rb><rt>ひとり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;one (person)</span></span>、<span class="vocab">堀田<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>堀田</rb><rt>ほった</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Hotta (a.k.a. Yama Arashi)</span></span><span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher (used here as a title)</span></span>に<span class="vocab">お目にかかりたい<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>目</rb><rt>め</rt></ruby>にかかりたい&nbsp;would like to see</span></span>てて<span class="vocab">お出でた<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>でた&nbsp;came (over)</span></span>ぞなもし。<span class="vocab">今<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今</rb><rt>いま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(just) now</span></span><span class="vocab">お宅<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>宅</rb><rt>たく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(your) residence</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">参じた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>参</rb><rt>さん</rt></ruby>じた&nbsp;visited; called (at)</span></span>のじゃが、<span class="vocab">お留守<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>留守</rb><rt>るす</rt></ruby>&nbsp;away; not home</span></span>じゃけれ、<span class="vocab">大方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大方</rb><rt>おおかた</rt></ruby>&nbsp;probably; most likely</span></span>ここじゃろうてて<span class="vocab">捜し当てて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>捜</rb><rt>さが</rt></ruby>し<ruby><rb>当</rb><rt>あ</rt></ruby>てて&nbsp;search out</span></span>お出でたのじゃがなもしと、<span class="vocab">閾<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>閾</rb><rt>しきい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;threshold; doorsill</span></span>の<span class="vocab">所<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>所</rb><rt>ところ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;place; location</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">膝を突いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>膝</rb><rt>ひざ</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>突</rb><rt>つ</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;kneel down</span></span>山嵐の<span class="vocab">返事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>返事</rb><rt>へんじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;response</span></span>を<span class="vocab">待って<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>待</rb><rt>ま</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;await</span></span>る。山嵐はそうですかと<span class="vocab">玄関<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>玄関</rb><rt>げんかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;entry hall</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">出て行った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>て<ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;went out (to)</span></span>が、やがて<span class="vocab">帰って来て<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>って<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;came back</span></span>、<span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you (familiar)</span></span>、生徒が<span class="vocab">祝勝会<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>祝勝会</rb><rt>しゅくしょうかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;victory celebration</span></span>の<span class="vocab">余興<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>余興</rb><rt>よきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;entertainment program; festivities</span></span>を<span class="vocab">見に<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;to see</span></span>行かないかって<span class="vocab">誘いに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誘</rb><rt>さそ</rt></ruby>いに&nbsp;to invite</span></span>来たんだ。<span class="vocab">今日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today</span></span>は<span class="vocab">高知<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>高知</rb><rt>こうち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kōchi (city in southern part of Shikoku)</span></span>から、<span class="vocab">何とか<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>とか&nbsp;so-and-so; such-and-such</span></span><span class="vocab">踴り<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>踴</rb><rt>おど</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;dance</span></span>をしに、わざわざここまで<span class="vocab">多人数<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>多人数</rb><rt>たにんず</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a large contingent (of people)</span></span><span class="vocab">乗り込んで<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>乗</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>り<ruby><rb>込</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;arrived; made an entry</span></span>来ているのだから、<span class="vocab">是非<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>是非</rb><rt>ぜひ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;by all means</span></span><span class="vocab">見物しろ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見物</rb><rt>けんぶつ</rt></ruby>しろ&nbsp;come and see</span></span>、めったに見られない<span class="vocab">踴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>踴</rb><rt>おどり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dance</span></span>だというんだ、君もいっしょに行ってみたまえと山嵐は<span class="vocab">大いに<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>おお</rt></ruby>いに&nbsp;greatly</span></span><span class="vocab">乗り気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>乗</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>り<ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>&nbsp;interest; enthusiasm</span></span>で、おれに<span class="vocab">同行<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同行</rb><rt>どうこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;accompaniment; going with</span></span>を<span class="vocab">勧める<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>勧</rb><rt>すす</rt></ruby>める&nbsp;exhort; encourage</span></span>。おれは踴なら<span class="vocab">東京<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>東京</rb><rt>とうきょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tōkyō</span></span>でたくさん見ている。<span class="vocab">毎年<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>毎年</rb><rt>まいとし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;each year; every year</span></span><span class="vocab">八幡様<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>八幡様</rb><rt>はちまんさま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Hachiman Shrine</span></span>の<span class="vocab">お祭り<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>祭</rb><rt>まつ</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;festival</span></span>には<span class="vocab">屋台<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>屋台</rb><rt>やたい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;moving stage; dancing stage</span></span>が<span class="vocab">町内<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>町内</rb><rt>ちょうない</rt></ruby>&nbsp;town; neighborhood</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">廻ってくる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>廻</rb><rt>まわ</rt></ruby>ってくる&nbsp;come around (to)</span></span>んだから<span class="vocab">汐酌み<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>汐酌</rb><rt>しおく</rt></ruby>み&nbsp;shiokumi (dance)</span></span>でも何でもちゃんと<span class="vocab">心得ている<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>心得</rb><rt>こころえ</rt></ruby>ている&nbsp;have knowledge of; be familiar with</span></span>。<span class="vocab">土佐っぽ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>土佐</rb><rt>とさ</rt></ruby>っぽ&nbsp;folks from Tosa (present-day Kōchi Prefecture)</span></span>の<span class="vocab">馬鹿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>馬鹿</rb><rt>ばか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fool; idiot</span></span>踴なんか、見たくもないと<span class="vocab">思った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought</span></span>けれども、せっかく山嵐が勧めるもんだから、つい行く<span class="vocab">気<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>&nbsp;inclination</span></span>になって<span class="vocab">門<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>門</rb><rt>もん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;gate</span></span>へ出た。山嵐を誘いに来たものは<span class="vocab">誰か<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誰</rb><rt>だれ</rt></ruby>か&nbsp;who</span></span>と思ったら赤シャツの<span class="vocab">弟<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>弟</rb><rt>おとうと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;younger brother</span></span>だ。<span class="vocab">妙な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>妙</rb><rt>みょう</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;odd; strange</span></span><span class="vocab">奴<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>奴</rb><rt>やつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fellow</span></span>が来たもんだ。</p>

